comments: Washington (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Irving (BKN) and firms up to absorb the contact.
Washington (CHA) briefly places a hand/arm to the front of Curry (BKN) during the drive but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Drummond (BKN) moves into and makes contact with Bridges' (CHA) body while defending his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) defends the drive and makes marginal contact with Durant's (BKN) body on the play.
Washington (CHA) legally contests Durant (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Curry (BKN) places two hands on Martin's (CHA) body as he moves towards his picking position, the contact reroutes him.
Durant (BKN) places a hand to the front of Bridges (CHA) at the start of the drive but the contact is marginal.
Rozier (CHA) makes makes marginal contact to the arm of Irving (BKN) on the perimeter before the shot.
